print 'Thank you, enjoy your meal!'

points = 0
letters = a, b, c, d, e
repeat 10 times
    letter = letters at random
    print 'Press the letter ' letter
    if letter is pressed
        print 'great'
        points = points + 1
    else
        print 'oops wrong letter'
        points = points - 2

print points
